## Aggression Style

- Bluff frequency: low / medium / high
- 3-bet range: value-only / balanced (bluffs + value) / aggressive
- C-bet frequency: always / selective (board-texture driven) / rarely

---

## Bet Sizing Rules

| Situation            | Sizing       |
|----------------------|--------------|
| Preflop open         | 2.5× BB      |
| Preflop 3-bet        | 3× the open  |
| Dry flop c-bet       | 33% pot      |
| Wet flop c-bet       | 66% pot      |
| River value bet      | 66-75% pot   |
| River bluff          | 75% pot      |

